<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ᴄᴀʟᴀx ᴛᴜᴛᴏʀɪᴀʟs | ZIMSEC O & A Level</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            background: #f4f6f9; 
            color: #333; 
        }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }
        header { 
            background: #1a365d; 
            color: white; 
            padding: 40px 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
        }
        header h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        header p { font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.9; }
        .subjects { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); 
            gap: 20px; 
            margin: 30px 0; 
        }
        .card { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 25px; 
            border-radius: 10px; 
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-top: 4px solid #2b6cb0;
        }
        .card h3 { color: #1a365d; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .card ul { margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .btn { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: #25D366; 
            color: white; 
            padding: 15px 30px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            margin: 10px 5px;
        }
        .btn-call { background: #2b6cb0; }
        .contact { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 10px; 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        footer { 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 20px; 
            color: #666; 
            font-size: 0.9rem; 
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .btn { display: block; margin: 10px 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>ᴄᴀʟᴀx ᴛᴜᴛᴏʀɪᴀʟs</h1>
            <p>ZIMSEC O & A Level | Maths | Accounting | Computer Science</p>
            <p>Helping Zimbabwean students pass with distinction</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="subjects">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>📐 Mathematics</h3>
                <p>Build confidence in problem solving</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>O Level: Paper 1 & 2 strategies</li>
                    <li>A Level: Pure Math</li>
                    <li>Past exam question drills</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <h3>💰 Accounting</h3>
                <p>Master the numbers that matter</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>O Level: Principles to Final Accounts</li>
                    <li>A Level: Financial + Cost Accounting</li>
                    <li>ZIMSEC format & presentation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <h3>💻 Computer Science</h3>
                <p>From theory to practical coding</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>O Level: Theory + Programming basics</li>
                    <li>A Level: Algorithms + Database</li>
                    <li>Project guidance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="contact">
            <h2>Start Learning Today</h2>
            <p>Online via WhatsApp/Google Meet | One-on-one & group classes available</p>
            <p><strong>Fees:</strong> From $3/week group | $5week one-on-one</p>
            
            <!-- EDIT THESE 2 LINES WITH YOUR DETAILS -->
            <a href="https://wa.me/+263711496500?text=Hi%20Calax,%20I%20need%20tutorials%20for%20" class="btn">Message on WhatsApp</a>
            <a href="tel:+263785444523" class="btn btn-call">Call Now</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 ᴄᴀʟᴀx ᴛᴜᴛᴏʀɪᴀʟs | Harare, Zimbabwe | ZIMSEC focused tutoring</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
